, female (6–8—holotype, photos by Alyssa Seemann; 9–12—females from Ambo, Ethiopia; 6, 9—face and pronotum; 7, 10–11—lateral view; 8, 12—dorsal view); 13–15— 
<taxonomicName box="[238,401,1913,1937]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Macropsis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="368" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridofulgida">
